Dialogue: 10,0:02:30.99,0:02:31.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Gen's at it again!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:31.91,0:02:32.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:32.85,0:02:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Cut it out!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:33.84,0:02:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Hit him back!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:35.25,0:02:37.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone stop him!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:37.14,0:02:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Cut it out{,} already!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:38.16,0:02:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:38.84,0:02:40.14,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on here?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:40.75,0:02:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,That's enough!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:47.87,0:02:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Good grief.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:49.68,0:02:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,This time, it was with a much older boy.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:51.40,0:02:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,How in the world is he so strong?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:53.73,0:02:56.57,Default,,0,0,0,,And that temper of his... He's uncontrollable!{}
Dialogue: 10,0:02:56.57,0:02:58.77,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no telling what he might do next.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:58.77,0:03:00.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't even want to think about it.{The very thought sends chills down my spine.}
Dialogue: 10,0:03:06.32,0:03:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Gen!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:07.82,0:03:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened to your face?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:09.50,0:03:11.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you get in another fight?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:12.06,0:03:13.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Who was it this time?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:14.22,0:03:15.48,Default,,0,0,0,,They started it.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:16.05,0:03:18.18,Default,,0,0,0,,They were talking about me behind my back.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:19.74,0:03:21.18,Default,,0,0,0,,About Mom?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:21.74,0:03:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,They said it's all a lie{ that she's sick}.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:24.59,0:03:27.69,Default,,0,0,0,,They said she left because she hated me, \Nnot because she's sick.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:28.17,0:03:29.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course it's not a lie!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:30.41,0:03:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,If you behave,
Dialogue: 10,0:03:32.00,0:03:33.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom will get better soon and—
Dialogue: 10,0:03:33.19,0:03:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It {\i1}is{\i0} a lie!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:36.19,0:03:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,She got sick because she had me.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:39.48,0:03:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,No wonder she doesn't want to see me!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:41.20,0:03:42.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Gen! That's not true!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:44.91,0:03:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Please listen to your father for one second.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:48.22,0:03:52.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You're just so full of energy that she can hardly bear to see you while she's so ill.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:52.94,0:03:54.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You understand?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:57.57,0:03:58.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Gen...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:00.13,0:04:01.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you looking at?!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:01.89,0:04:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at me!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:07.58,0:04:08.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Gen!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:58.88,0:05:00.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What is this?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:04.72,0:05:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's got so many colors, and they're all moving around...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:08.21,0:05:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's like it's alive.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:15.69,0:05:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's so pretty.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:21.23,0:05:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But it's probably something else I'm not supposed to see...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:29.18,0:05:30.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}just like those.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:35.42,0:05:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If I tell him I saw this, he'll get angry again.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:50.25,0:05:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,There's someone up there{,} in the sky.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:56.29,0:05:59.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad, is that an angel?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:02.35,0:06:04.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Gen, you...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:06.51,0:06:07.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't talk nonsense.{}
Dialogue: 10,0:06:07.76,0:06:08.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You're imagining things.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:10.27,0:06:11.54,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's right there.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:12.03,0:06:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't see things like that.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:15.60,0:06:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Things like that...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:17.73,0:06:18.94,Default,,0,0,0,,don't exist.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:36.13,0:06:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:39.01,0:06:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{That's weird. }It doesn't have any seams.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:46.30,0:06:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I read somewhere that angels wear clothes that don't have any seams.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:59.52,0:07:01.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Maybe...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:02.93,0:07:05.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}this is what she's been searching for.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:16.21,0:07:18.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, Gen! Cut it out{,} already!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:18.61,0:07:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Cut it out!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:19.32,0:07:21.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone go get a grown-up!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:30.03,0:07:31.47,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're Gen, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:32.71,0:07:34.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You've gotten pretty big{ and strong}.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:37.21,0:07:38.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:41.28,0:07:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I met you once, back when you were just a baby.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:44.78,0:07:47.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Hard to believe such a scrawny thing grew up like this.{..}
Dialogue: 10,0:07:48.61,0:07:49.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{Is }There something you want?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:50.56,0:07:52.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You have a strange robe at your home, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:57.63,0:08:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the one who brought you it.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:07.55,0:08:11.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard that your child is unwell as of late.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:15.87,0:08:17.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:17.03,0:08:18.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You were right to be worried.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:27.44,0:08:29.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:29.17,0:08:31.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I am clothing him in a special robe.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:33.77,0:08:36.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Until he regains his strength,
Dialogue: 10,0:08:36.53,0:08:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,please leave this robe on him.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:40.00,0:08:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What robe?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:42.40,0:08:44.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't lie to me.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:44.03,0:08:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing there.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:47.02,0:08:49.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Gen! You finally opened your eyes...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:50.19,0:08:53.35,Default,,0,0,0,,For now, would you consider just seeing how things go?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:55.60,0:08:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,No need for thanks until after he's grown into a fine boy.{Keep this comment: NB: This is a good forum post on the use of "until" with "after": http://ell.stackexchange.com/questions/22389/whats-the-difference-between-until-and-until-after . In this sentence, Ginko is emphasizing that thanks aren't due now, but later. I therefore added the "after" as an intensifier, intended to emphasize the whole point of the line.}
Dialogue: 10,0:09:01.28,0:09:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's how it went.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:06.64,0:09:09.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like it may have worked a bit {\i1}too{\i0} well, though.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:09.85,0:09:13.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't control yourself when you get mad, can you?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:15.60,0:09:18.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You're probably in need of a bit of mushi-severing.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:18.61,0:09:19.64,Default,,0,0,0,,"Mushi"?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:22.35,0:09:25.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Your affinity for mushi has become too strong.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:25.98,0:09:28.05,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're a child with such a strong affinity,
Dialogue: 10,0:09:28.48,0:09:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,you may have some difficulty \Ncontrolling yourself when you're mad.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:32.17,0:09:33.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't want that, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:34.25,0:09:35.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Then give me your hand.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:38.16,0:09:42.14,Default,,0,0,0,,If you do this, will I lose the ability to see her too?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:43.05,0:09:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. But if you don't want that, \NI just won't go through with it all the way.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:01.01,0:10:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hm?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:02.96,0:10:04.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's not coming out...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:08.11,0:10:11.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, typically, it should come out through your fingertips, but...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:13.04,0:10:14.30,Default,,0,0,0,,That's weird.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:19.60,0:10:20.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It's you!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:25.93,0:10:28.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Your son's grown into a fine boy.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:30.51,0:10:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm grateful that he's in good health,
Dialogue: 10,0:10:33.50,0:10:35.49,Default,,0,0,0,,but he can be so unruly.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:36.59,0:10:39.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Back then, I was willing to grasp at any chance of saving him...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:41.13,0:10:44.17,Default,,0,0,0,,but are you the one responsible \Nfor the way Gen is now?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:45.85,0:10:48.87,Default,,0,0,0,,That day, what exactly was it that you did to him?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:51.13,0:10:53.51,Default,,0,0,0,,She asked me not to tell you, but...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:54.75,0:10:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,back then, before I came to your house,
Dialogue: 10,0:10:58.21,0:11:00.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I met his mother.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:02.22,0:11:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,She's the one who made that robe.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:29.04,0:11:29.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:31.61,0:11:33.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What is that robe?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:36.64,0:11:38.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What a beautiful robe.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:39.82,0:11:42.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Out of curiosity, might I ask how you came to possess it?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:43.47,0:11:48.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You can see that kimono?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:53.53,0:11:58.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I wove it myself, from thread I spun.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:59.90,0:12:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,But even so, I have no clue \Nwhat the thread is made out of.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:07.05,0:12:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Years ago, I suddenly became able to see things.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:14.03,0:12:18.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It happened after I gave birth \Nto my little boy and nearly died from it.{The first "It" should be clear from the dialogue, and although a little vaguer, the second "it" seems to clearly enough refer back to "giving birth."}
Dialogue: 10,0:12:26.91,0:12:28.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yui?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:28.65,0:12:29.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yui!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:29.59,0:12:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You're finally awake!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:31.36,0:12:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,,How are you feeling?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:34.03,0:12:35.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Is our baby...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:36.25,0:12:37.49,Default,,0,0,0,,He's fine.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:37.49,0:12:39.07,Default,,0,0,0,,A healthy baby boy.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:39.87,0:12:41.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank goodness.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:41.51,0:12:42.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is he?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:42.66,0:12:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to hold him.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:45.68,0:12:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Yui, you've been asleep for several days.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:50.48,0:12:52.47,Default,,0,0,0,,So I took him back to our home.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:52.99,0:12:55.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll bring him to see you soon,
Dialogue: 10,0:12:55.01,0:12:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,so until then, just focus on regaining \Nyour strength here at your family home.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:00.53,0:13:02.07,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:12.67,0:13:15.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, Mom?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:15.36,0:13:16.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:17.53,0:13:21.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel as though I've been reborn.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:24.62,0:13:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,The world looks like an entirely different place.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:45.68,0:13:50.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Have the trees and the grass always been so radiant?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:04.48,0:14:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:08.27,0:14:10.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What is this thread?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:12.06,0:14:15.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Whatever it is, it's beautiful.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:21.13,0:14:23.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Yui, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:24.35,0:14:26.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't this thread beautiful?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:26.98,0:14:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I may be getting a bit ahead of myself,
Dialogue: 10,0:14:29.12,0:14:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,but I thought I could make \Nsomething special for Gen to wear{ on special occasions}.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:32.38,0:14:33.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Thread?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:34.03,0:14:39.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom, did you ever know you could harvest \Nsuch beautiful thread from the trees around here?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:40.88,0:14:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:44.86,0:14:47.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't strain yourself too much, okay?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:56.64,0:14:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Gen...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:58.03,0:15:00.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, how I've wanted to meet you!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:02.29,0:15:04.39,Default,,0,0,0,,She seems much better.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:04.96,0:15:07.22,Default,,0,0,0,,How is Yui doing lately?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:08.06,0:15:12.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, there are still some things that worry me.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:14.53,0:15:18.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Every now and then, she says very strange things.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:20.45,0:15:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ah...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:23.20,0:15:26.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's glowing just like the trees.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:28.00,0:15:31.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He looks so wonderful.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:39.28,0:15:40.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Gen?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:40.75,0:15:42.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Gen!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:42.80,0:15:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:44.46,0:15:46.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Dear, Gen's...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:46.23,0:15:48.26,Default,,0,0,0,,He suddenly went limp.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:49.23,0:15:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:50.85,0:15:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:52.56,0:15:56.74,Default,,0,0,0,,When I caressed him, \Nthis shining thread came out, and then...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:57.26,0:15:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:58.64,0:15:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Give him to me!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:59.76,0:16:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to get him to a doctor!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:01.20,0:16:02.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll come with you!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:02.40,0:16:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{You can}Just stay here!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:44.59,0:16:47.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It seemed as though it was shedding its skin.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:49.41,0:16:54.07,Default,,0,0,0,,That was the moment when I realized it was alive.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:54.77,0:16:59.33,Default,,0,0,0,,If only I had never touched those threads...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:01.10,0:17:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,,My poor baby boy... What's going to happen to him?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:07.21,0:17:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,This is unexpected.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:10.03,0:17:14.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Those threads of yours are \Nwhat we mushi-shi call the ether.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:16.14,0:17:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It's also what triggered your sudden ability \Nto see things you were unable to see before.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:22.59,0:17:28.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}But this is my first time hearing of someone able to spin it into \Nthread without using any medicine and using only their fingers.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:28.61,0:17:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What happens when you remove it from someone?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:31.04,0:17:32.31,Default,,0,0,0,,What will happen to my son?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:33.93,0:17:36.62,Default,,0,0,0,,A fully grown child wouldn't be very affected,
Dialogue: 10,0:17:37.52,0:17:40.86,Default,,0,0,0,,but infants, on the other hand, need the ether to live.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:41.69,0:17:43.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Most are born with what they need.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:45.93,0:17:49.16,Default,,0,0,0,,However, if too much is extracted from them, they lose their vitality.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:50.35,0:17:51.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:54.05,0:17:57.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't there something I can do to save him?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:58.08,0:17:59.64,Default,,0,0,0,,There is one way.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:01.17,0:18:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,If we put this robe on him, he may live.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:11.87,0:18:13.83,Default,,0,0,0,,The results of which you well know.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:14.67,0:18:17.41,Default,,0,0,0,,He's grown into a very healthy boy, twice as strong as any his age.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:17.41,0:18:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,However, he now has too {\i1}much{\i0} ether.{...rather than "too little," which is how much he had before.}
Dialogue: 10,0:18:22.06,0:18:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Under normal circumstances, \Nmushi-shi can extract it using medicine.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:25.68,0:18:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,But that has no effect on him.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:29.31,0:18:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I know you may find all this a bit difficult to believe,
Dialogue: 10,0:18:32.62,0:18:35.78,Default,,0,0,0,,but perhaps you should talk to your son \Nand let him see his mother.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:37.31,0:18:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,,With how things have progressed, she may \Nvery well be the only one who can extract his ether.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:43.97,0:18:45.38,Default,,0,0,0,,That's impossible.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:47.74,0:18:48.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:50.67,0:18:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,All this time, Mom didn't hate me after all.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:56.75,0:19:00.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to see Mom.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:03.95,0:19:06.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Gen, I'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:08.48,0:19:12.44,Default,,0,0,0,,If only I had let you see her earlier...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:21.12,0:19:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,She's been like this for almost two years.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:25.45,0:19:28.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like she's turned into an empty shell.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:29.81,0:19:33.24,Default,,0,0,0,,If only I had forgiven her sooner...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:34.61,0:19:36.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She must have continued spinning the thread,
Dialogue: 10,0:19:37.84,0:19:40.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}probably in an attempt to make another robe.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:42.37,0:19:46.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She's been exposed to so much ether \Nthat she's fallen under the mushi's influence.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:48.30,0:19:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I should've paid more attention to her and not just her son.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:52.72,0:19:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it, Gen?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:54.85,0:19:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I know her.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:57.85,0:19:59.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You remember her?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:59.36,0:20:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,No, that's not what I mean.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:01.60,0:20:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,She's the angel who's been \Nwatching over me all this time!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:07.18,0:20:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That day, they took her back home with them.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:15.33,0:20:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}After some time, vitality returned to her body.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:21.76,0:20:23.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom, can you hear me?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:30.61,0:20:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Around that time,
Dialogue: 10,0:20:32.93,0:20:35.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}the angel vanished.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:37.28,0:20:41.68,Default,,0,0,0,,One day, I suddenly felt my body grow very light,
Dialogue: 10,0:20:42.54,0:20:46.17,Default,,0,0,0,,and before I knew it, I found myself watching him from the sky.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:47.74,0:20:52.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I was so happy to see him growing so well.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:52.65,0:20:53.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:55.02,0:20:56.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry, Yui.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:57.84,0:21:00.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be. I'm sorry too.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:06.05,0:21:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,As we agreed,
Dialogue: 10,0:21:07.54,0:21:09.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to take this robe.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:10.29,0:21:13.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure that's all you need?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:13.16,0:21:14.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It's more than enough.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:14.79,0:21:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,,A robe like this is exceedingly rare.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:18.86,0:21:21.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you still see the threads of light?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:22.40,0:21:24.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, not anymore.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:25.92,0:21:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:27.42,0:21:28.93,Default,,0,0,0,,That's for the best for you.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:29.71,0:21:33.93,Default,,0,0,0,,But what shall I do about him?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:33.93,0:21:34.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:34.85,0:21:37.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Guess I'll have to develop a more potent medicine...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:48.22,0:21:49.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What's this?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:50.51,0:21:53.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hm, guess there's no need for that medicine anymore.
